All right, you have your tea.
Now let's get you set up

06:58.935 --> 07:00.307
in the library.
- You mean the room

07:00.308 --> 07:02.074
with the books
I can literally see from here?

07:02.110 --> 07:03.120
Joy, I don't need
to have any attitude.

07:03.144 --> 07:08.214
I can set myself up, Dad,
thanks.

07:09.249 --> 07:11.416
These associates get younger

07:11.451 --> 07:13.451
and angrier, don't they?
- That's not an associate;

07:13.487 --> 07:14.564
that's my daughter.
- And you think

07:14.588 --> 07:16.221
I didn't know that?

07:16.256 --> 07:18.123
I can spot
a ninth-grade pushback

07:18.158 --> 07:19.991
from a mile away.

07:20.027 --> 07:22.005
Let me ask you something:
how'd you manage your kids?

07:22.029 --> 07:24.529
- What do you mean, manage 'em?
- I mean, Joy got in trouble

07:24.564 --> 07:26.097
at school,
that's why she's here.

07:26.133 --> 07:27.665
And she may be a pain
in the ass,

07:27.701 --> 07:29.345
but she finishes her homework
in 18 seconds

07:29.369 --> 07:30.680
and all I have today
is paperwork.

07:30.704 --> 07:31.936
I got it.

07:31.972 --> 07:34.072
Your daughter won't listen
and you don't want

07:34.107 --> 07:36.141
to talk to her, anyway.
- No, I just don't know

07:36.176 --> 07:37.453
what to say to her
to get her to hear me.

07:37.477 --> 07:39.310
That's because sometimes
there is no way

07:39.346 --> 07:40.211
to get them to hear you.

07:40.247 --> 07:42.080
But they might
hear someone else.

07:42.115 --> 07:44.516
Someone--someone cool.

07:44.551 --> 07:46.418
- Someone like you?
- No, no, no.

07:46.453 --> 07:48.319
Not me.
- Come on, Gretchen,

07:48.355 --> 07:50.266
what's it gonna take?
- I'm not saying I won't do it.

07:50.290 --> 07:51.723
I'm saying it won't work.
- Why not?

07:51.758 --> 07:55.493
Because it can't be someone
you think is cool...

07:55.529 --> 07:57.195
It has to be someone
she thinks is cool.

07:57.230 --> 07:58.930
Well, look at that.

07:58.965 --> 08:00.532
Maybe you're not doomed
after all.

08:00.567 --> 08:02.000
Now, move out of the way.

08:02.035 --> 08:03.968
I gotta get me some
of that almond milk.

